{"tid":2172474,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"戴口罩也要很性感！童顏人妻「街頭解放」胸前僅剩2片薄布","createTime":"2020-08-24T15:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T16:02:58.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7a5639301266ac2072ec52f9d952568d52acb111","tid":2172474,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:38:32.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎（COVID-19、新冠肺炎）疫情席捲全球，鄰近台灣的南韓疫情嚴重，也讓外出配戴口罩，幾乎成了一項全民運動。近期，南韓29歲網紅人妻申才恩（신재은，Zenny）就分享了一張戴口罩的「街頭解放」美照，引發粉絲迴響。<br />\n<br />\n29歲的申才恩的童顏外表，像極了10多歲的少女，結合她白皙渾圓的上圍，儼然成為「童顏巨乳」一詞的最佳代言人。經常在IG分享美圖與生活動態的申才恩，近期就披露了一張令人臉紅心跳的街頭美拍。<br />\n<br />\n從照片中可看出，為了響應防疫，申才恩特別戴上白色口罩外出，她還褪下了穿在外頭的長版外套，對著鏡頭秀出穿著純白比基尼的好身材，胸、腰、腿三大曲線展露無疑。其中，她飽滿的身材，似乎讓比基尼有些包不住，溢出來的「北半球」，增添幾分性感氣息。<br />\n<br />\n除了身材之外，申才恩兩張照片一張採取「微俯視」的表情，另一張則是轉頭看向另一邊，與以往的甜美微笑向比，這次拍攝讓人看到有別以往的高冷氣質，讓粉絲們紛紛留言「超美」、「超性感」。"},{"pid":"d548da5a171f9baf8d9960e54fb8fe5ca78d49d7","tid":2172474,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:38:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/24/2736472-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F24%2F2736472-PH.jpg&h=97e88d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲申才恩街頭解放好身材。（圖／翻攝自zennyrt IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/24/2736473-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F24%2F2736473-PH.jpg&h=5666524c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cc1622b82ed3ac573872acd80a95bd880bd4583d","tid":2172474,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/09/2710753-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F09%2F2710753-PH.jpg&h=aa36bc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲申才恩美圖。（圖／翻攝自zennyrt IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/12/2549582-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2F2549582-PH.jpg&h=b260c2ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bfc838dbea824591a88080df5025af9072fca6e","tid":2172474,"uid":371171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc1622b82ed3ac573872acd80a95bd880bd4583d","tid":2172474,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:39:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/08/09/2710753-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F08%2F09%2F2710753-PH.jpg&h=aa36bc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲申才恩美圖。（圖／翻攝自zennyrt IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/12/2549582-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F12%2F2549582-PH.jpg&h=b260c2ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:40:39.000Z","msg":"扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc6075cda609e484cd103a52affb9ff5a9f52b4","tid":2172474,"uid":266467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:41:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f513ba01dd2244b55f2df7d8512b25524ac97bb3","tid":2172474,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:41:45.000Z","msg":"camel toe 都突哂出來"},{"pid":"6cd0e872f1381411c46b83ddd371495465999eea","tid":2172474,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:42:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc724455faf2cdb04e2c4e7a55e81c011c53898f","tid":2172474,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0